            <div
                class="archive-feature__image"
                style="--image: url('https://www.playboy.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Playboy-PB-Online-Spring-2026-Our-Past-Playmates-in-the-Reunion-of-a-Lifetime-Nadia-Lee-Cohen-Hero-1200x939.jpg');"
            >
                <div class="archive-feature__eyebrow">FROM THE ARCHIVES</div>
