        <div class="archive-feature__content">
                            <div class="archive-feature__date">
                    Winter 2019                </div>
                        <div class="archive-feature__headline">
                Our Past Playmates, in the Reunion of a Lifetime            </div>
                            <div class="archive-feature__description">
                    This Women's History Month, we're revisiting Jamilah Lemieux's examination of the Playmate franchise's evolution, featuring photography by Nadia Lee Cohen.                </div>
                        <a
                class="archive-feature__button"
                href="https://www.playboy.com/read/our-past-playmates-in-the-reunion-of-a-lifetime/"
                                            >
                Read More            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
